         <div type="entry" xml:id="lc.1805-04-03.03">
            <sp who="jo">
               <speaker>Ordway</speaker>
               <ab>
                  <date/>
               </ab>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Wednesday 3rd April 1805</hi>.    clear and pleasant. The
          articles which was to be Sent back to the States in the Big Barge was packed and boxed
          up ready to go on board.</p>
            </sp>
